<p><strong>Saving Throws</strong> Wis +6, Cha +4</p>

<p><strong>Skills</strong> Deception +4, History +2, Religion +2</p>

<p><strong>Languages</strong> Common, Draconic, Infernal</p>

<p><strong>Challenge</strong> 2 (450 XP)</p>

<p><strong><em>Spellcasting.</em></strong> Frulam is a 5th-level spellcaster that uses Wisdom as her spellcasting ability (spell save DC 14, +6 to hit with spell attacks). Frulam has the following spells prepared from the cleric spell list:</p>

<ul>
  <li>
    <p>Cantrips (at will): light, sacred flame, thaumaturgy</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>1st level (4 slots): command, cure wounds, healing word, sanctuary</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>2nd level (3 slots): calm emotions, hold person, spiritual weapon</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>3rd level (2 slots): mass healing word, spirit guardians</p>
  </li>
</ul>

<p><strong>Actions</strong></p>

<p><strong><em>Multiattack.</em></strong> Frulam attacks twice with her halberd.</p>

<p><strong><em>Halberd.</em></strong> Melee Weapon Attack: +5 to hit, reach 10 ft., one target. Hit: 7 (1d10 + 2) bludgeoning damage.</p>

